@node main
@title "TAPAVI 1.5 Copyright © 1994,1995 by John Bickers"

                              TAPAVI 1.5
                  Copyright © 1994,1995 by John Bickers.

    This is a residentable AVI animation player for 020+ machines with
    KS 2.0 or better, for the Picasso II graphics board.

    @{" Requirements        " link "requirements"}
    @{" Supported Encoding  " link "encoding"    }

    @{" CLI Parameters      " link "cli"         }
    @{" Workbench ToolTypes " link "wb"          }
    @{" Operation           " link "operation"   }

    @{" XAnim               " link "xanim"       }
    @{" CD-ROMs             " link "cd-roms"     }

    @{" Credits             " link "credits"     }
